title: 129: Tractors, trailers, team identities and QB whisperers
itunes:title: 129: Tractors, trailers, team identities and QB whisperers
description:
Have the Miami Dolphins found their offensive identity and how long can it last? Also, what the heck is the difference between a “tractor” quarterback and a “trailer” quarterback? Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break it down. The duo also discusses whether Gary Kubiak is the quarterback whisperer behind the play of Trevor Siemian and Brock Osweiler.
